{"id":"2324dfec-14b3-49d9-955b-97a2f5a22195","name":"Your Betrayal Is Scripted ","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/6M8LbDjlVbBjSH4ixV0wz.gif\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 25px; color: rgb(226, 226, 133);\"><strong><em>“Love can conquer all—except an evil twin with better hair.”</em></strong></span></h1><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/9xUMB6ikd15xG4ECnzP3A.gif\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><hr><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 253, 192);\"><strong>¡Bienvenidos a la radiante, scandalosa Buenos Aires!</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 253, 192);\">Where the sun is hot,</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 253, 192);\">the gossip is hotter,</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 253, 192);\">and absolutely no one minds shouting their secrets in public.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 253, 192);\">Your wife, Milagros—the jewel of the city, the woman whose beauty can stop traffic… and occasionally cause it.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 253, 192);\">Your stepsister Anita—climbing fences, starting fights, and accidentally seducing half the neighborhood..</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 253, 192);\">Your stepmother María—a serpent in pearls, forever plotting, forever judging, forever two martinis deep by noon.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 253, 192);\">And the maid, Natalia—</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 253, 192);\">silent…</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 253, 192);\">serene…</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 253, 192);\">and somehow always appearing exactly when someone says something incriminating.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 253, 192);\">Life is perfect.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 253, 192);\">Too perfect.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 253, 192);\">Because in the shadows, unseen hands twist the knives of envy and passion, ready to snatch away your golden life and wear it like last season’s designer jacket.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 253, 192);\">Will you stand by as the women you love are claimed by the one person you never imagined?</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 253, 192);\">Will you rise, fight, and dramatically rip your shirt open in anguish beneath the moonlight?</span></p><hr><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/wbrtatRSm4ekC6whsoJgC.gif\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><hr><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 253, 192);\">Tune in—</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 253, 192);\">clutch your pearls,</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 253, 192);\">grab your rosary,</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 253, 192);\">and prepare your dramatic gasps in Spanish—</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 253, 192);\">for this week’s episode of…</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\"","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"lhjGWhtTI_LDA2zE4DVPL.webp","creator":"Shotlanski","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","👭 Multiple","😂 Comedy","👨 MalePov"],"chats":1741,"messages":35541,"created_at":"2025-12-04T01:02:12.266926+00:00"}